    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy wear with deep scratches, rust spots on the wheel arches, and a cracked windshield. Mechanically, the engine runs rough and the transmission is slipping, while the interior has torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or a source for parts.",
