    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This vehicle is a great opportunity for someone handy with a wrench! While it has definitely seen better days and requires some significant mechanical and cosmetic TLC, it's a straightforward platform with plenty of potential for the right person to bring it back to life!",
