    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant wear, including advanced rust on the rear quarter panels, several deep dents, and a cracked windshield that will need replacement. Inside, the upholstery is heavily stained and torn in multiple places, and several dashboard components are loose or non-functional. Mechanically, the engine starts but has a noticeable oil leak, and the tires are near the end of their life, meaning the car will require immediate maintenance and repairs to be reliable.",
