    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the pristine exterior finish to the untouched interior appointments. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, this motorcar offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. It is, without qualification, a benchmark of automotive excellence.",
